ontent","Documentary style films","Commercial/advertising content","Scientific/research documentation","Conservation stories"],"learning_approach":["Group workshops (within a group of approx. 10 persons)","Mixed approach (combination of group and individual)","Project-based learning (within a BTM project)"],"marine_subjects":["Coral reefs","Big marine life (sharks, whales, etc.)","Macro subjects","Marine behavior","Conservation stories"],"time_availability":"2-3 entire weeks at a time for a workshop, aproject or individual training","travel_willingness":"Yes, willing to travel internationally","budget":"Moderate budget (1,000 - 3,000 €/USD)","start_timeline":"Ready to start immediately","ultimate_vision":"To travel around create, showing others and inspiring them to do so.","inspiration_to_apply":"I mossed it whe. You guys came to maldives as i had other booked works and i would love to be with amazing people. As of now i did all alone.","referral_source":["Social Media (Instagram, Facebook, etc.)"],"questions_or_concerns":"Thanks","anything_else":"Any trip soon to maldives?"}'::jsonb, '{}', '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-01T01:12:10+00:00');
