oach":["Group workshops (within a group of approx. 10 persons)","Small group workshop (within a group of approx. 4 persons)","Mixed approach (combination of group and individual)"],"marine_subjects":["Big marine life (sharks, whales, etc.)","Marine behavior","Conservation stories"],"time_availability":"2-3 entire weeks at a time for a workshop, aproject or individual training","travel_willingness":"Yes, willing to travel internationally","budget":"Advanced budget (3,000 - 6,000 €/USD)","start_timeline":"Flexible/Not sure yet","ultimate_vision":"I love marine life in all its forms, but I’m especially passionate about big animals and stories of conservation and animal behavior. I’d love to keep improving my filming skills so maybe one day I can do this more professionally. I’ve never taken any underwater filmmaking courses or had a mentor. Everything I know is self-taught, so I’d really appreciate some professional guidance.","inspiration_to_apply":"I really like the way videos are presented on social media, especially the editing style, color grading, and the techniques used to tell the story.","referral_source":["Social Media (Instagram, Facebook, etc.)"]}'::jsonb, '{}', '[]'::jsonb, '2026-01-26T16:15:52+00:00');
