mary_goal":"Improve content creation for social media","secondary_goal":"Transform hobby into professional career","learning_aspects":["Marine life behavior understanding","Composition and content planning","Post-production and editing","Business aspects of underwater photography","Conservation documentation"],"content_to_create":["Personal/travel memories","Social media content","Documentary style photo series","Conservation stories"],"learning_approach":["Small group workshop (within a group of approx. 4 persons)","One-on-one mentorship","Mixed approach (combination of group and individual)"],"marine_subjects":["Big marine life (sharks, whales, etc.)"],"time_availability":"1 week to 10 days for a workshop, a project or individual training","travel_willingness":"Depends on duration and location","start_timeline":"Flexible/Not sure yet","ultimate_vision":"Freediving or Scuba diving with sharks, whales, mantas in the deep blue.","inspiration_to_apply":"My Motivations for \"Behind-the-mask\"\n\n **Professional Development**\n- Perfect underwater photography techniques and freediving skills for better shot opportunities\n\n **Awareness & Communication**\n- Bring the underwater world closer to people through your photos and inspire global audiences\n\n **Creative & Social Projects**\n- Showcase your work through photo exhibitions and support children''s projects\n\n **Conservation Impact**\n- Promote marine and nature conservation through visual documentation and advocacy","referral_source":["Social Media (Instagram, Facebook, etc.)"],"questions_or_concerns":"No","anything_else":"—"}'::jsonb, '{}', '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-11T17:12:08+00:00');
