","travel_willingness":"Yes, willing to travel internationally","budget":"Moderate budget (1,000 - 3,000 €/USD)","start_timeline":"Within next 3 months","ultimate_vision":"I don''t know how to put it I in words, it''s just that immense connection with one''s true self and being fully alive and free.. I wish I could make everyone feel that. I always feel home underwater that I can or able to literally breathe without a tank or a mask I''m just home. A place that I''ve had lived and experienced many many past lives before.","inspiration_to_apply":"Everything you do is aspiring and genuine. I just believe in u","referral_source":["Social media"]}'::jsonb, '{}', '[]'::jsonb, '2026-03-24T21:49:59+00:00');
